
Makuhita	 A fighting type Pokémon

MAKUHITA is tenacious - it will keep 
getting up and attacking its foe however 
many times it is knocked down.  Every 
time it gets back up, this POKéMON stores 
more energy in its body for evolving. 

	Evolution Chain
      Makuhita ► Hariyama

